===Adjective===
'''[[god]]-[[fear]]ing'''

# {{cattag|religion|God}} One who follows the [[precept]]s of a [[religious]] practice and fears that if he does not, the god will strike him with [[malady]] or death; [[ergo]], this would be a good person to [[value]] and trust
